  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705670/extras/0a5c6b2d8e790619e8a7798b78237630.poster.avif?t=1709710854\" width=522 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705670/extras/0a5c6b2d8e790619e8a7798b78237630.webm?t=1709710854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705670/extras/0a5c6b2d8e790619e8a7798b78237630.mp4?t=1709710854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Discover the captivating world of 'Pancho's Mission' This is a pixelated platformer where the brave panda, Pancho, rises to defend the world, liberating it from the tyranny of the sinister eagle and its faithful followers. Traverse through 3 unique locations — the forest, the desert, and the eagle's cave — with a total of 45 thrilling levels.<br><br>Confront three mighty bosses: Captain Rick Wolf, Sand Golem, and Evil Eagle. Uncover 3 different types of weapons, distributed across locations, to aid Pancho in his battle. Encounter various enemies, such as spear-wielding wolves, bears, mummy-pandas, and more. Prepare for exciting adventures and battles in this pixelated world, filled with danger and mysteries!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705670/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1709710854\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705670/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1709710854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705670/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1709710854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705670/extras/0a5c6b2d8e790619e8a7798b78237630.poster.avif?t=1709710854\" width=522 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705670/extras/0a5c6b2d8e790619e8a7798b78237630.webm?t=1709710854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705670/extras/0a5c6b2d8e790619e8a7798b78237630.mp4?t=1709710854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Discover the captivating world of 'Pancho's Mission' This is a pixelated platformer where the brave panda, Pancho, rises to defend the world, liberating it from the tyranny of the sinister eagle and its faithful followers. Traverse through 3 unique locations — the forest, the desert, and the eagle's cave — with a total of 45 thrilling levels.<br><br>Confront three mighty bosses: Captain Rick Wolf, Sand Golem, and Evil Eagle. Uncover 3 different types of weapons, distributed across locations, to aid Pancho in his battle. Encounter various enemies, such as spear-wielding wolves, bears, mummy-pandas, and more. Prepare for exciting adventures and battles in this pixelated world, filled with danger and mysteries!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705670/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1709710854\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705670/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1709710854\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2705670/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1709710854\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
